uding livestock) in its raw or natural state.” See Codification note above and Effective and Termination Dates of 2009 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–5","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1881(2), 1893, temporarily amended par. (2) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The term ‘agricultural commodity producer’ has the same meaning as the term ‘person’ as prescribed by regulations promulgated under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1308/e"},"text":"section 1308(e) of title 7","children":[],"tail":" (before the amendment made by section 1603(a) of the Food, Conservation, and Energy Act of 2008).” See Codification note above and Effective and Termination Dates of 2009 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (7). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–5","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1881(3), 1893, temporarily added par. (7). See Codification note above and Effective and Termination Dates of 2009 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s1603/g/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 1603(g)(6)","children":[],"tail":", as amended by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/79/s1609/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–79, § 1609(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “(before the amendment made by section 1603(a) of the Food, Conservation, and Energy Act of 2008)” before period at end."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/280"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–280","children":[],"tail":" substituted “1308(e)” for “1308(5)”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id05d5783d-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":